Hi @ingerul93 unfortunately IIRC we don't generally support Android Studio canary builds.  If you go back to 3.4 or Android Studio 3.5 beta 1, you should be fine again.

@stevemessick: have I got this right?

> we don't generally support Android Studio canary builds

OK, I'm actually not sure this is accurate.  Looking at the history we've supported a bunch in the past.  @stevemessick can probably clarify though.
You're welcome.  Thanks for the report! ðŸŽ‰
This was fixed in M36. As @pq said, we do not officially support the canary channel. When we can make it work, we do.
